author: NPR Music
description:
We received a record number of entries to this year's Tiny Desk Contest — nearly 7,500! Before we announce the winner, meet some of the talented unsigned artists of the 2025 Contest community. 

Soundtrack:
“Lemon Trader,” World Islaand
“Move My Feet,” calmestevieray & Wyatt Woodley
“Brick by Brick,” Lila Forde

Watch these entries and more: npr.org/tinydeskcontest

title: Meet the 2025 Tiny Desk Contest Community
